    "description": "<strong>Welcome to Red Rock. Will you survive the onslaught of <i>A-EYE</i> enemy drones?</strong><br><br>Battle Drones: Red Rock Resistance is a 3D top-down shooter set in a reimagined version of Red Rock, New Mexico. It's the post-drone war era, a supposed time of peace. Find yourself in the desert equipped with nothing more than a military drone, a handgun and a knife to fend off the incoming waves of hostile drones sent from the evil megacorporation <i>A-EYE</i>. Luckily, famous drone parts salesman Solomon Burgundy has a shop nearby! You’ll be sure to pay him a visit if you need new guns, ammo and even drone insurance!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/b51e91bcd2bc0925020c7b9768d82cf7.webp?t=1719456535\" width=616 height=44 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/681825a395ba6baed1e74ed37762a095.poster.avif?t=1719456535\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/681825a395ba6baed1e74ed37762a095.webm?t=1719456535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/681825a395ba6baed1e74ed37762a095.mp4?t=1719456535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Jump straight into action against the relentless <i>A-EYE</i>! Piloting a drone requires strategy and skill, there’s little time to relax between the endless waves. Are you up for the challenge?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/994a6c6ce2adabc97b3744940ed98806.webp?t=1719456535\" width=616 height=44 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/fde1fdab3fb8added32cd1cd6bc7af09.poster.avif?t=1719456535\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/fde1fdab3fb8added32cd1cd6bc7af09.webm?t=1719456535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/fde1fdab3fb8added32cd1cd6bc7af09.mp4?t=1719456535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Uncover a wide array of unique weapons and throwables; sharpened katanas, powerful shotguns, devastating dynamite and much more! Don’t forget to grab your drone upgrades too, Solomon’s Insurance is gonna come in handy when you get yourself into trouble…<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/2409406ea9d31e8bcddf100ee22f163f.webp?t=1719456535\" width=616 height=44 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/faebb34c7745864f0c01ca93da10cc67.poster.avif?t=1719456535\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/faebb34c7745864f0c01ca93da10cc67.webm?t=1719456535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/faebb34c7745864f0c01ca93da10cc67.mp4?t=1719456535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Don’t be fooled. They may seem like bots, but those pesky <i>A-EYE</i> keep developing their own new combat techniques. You’ll have to keep on your toes as they come at you with various weapons and mechanics.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/bf4980c76ca2eba428f74c58571ba6ea.webp?t=1719456535\" width=616 height=44 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/caaf5bc4188bc6f968096f6cc9c52d0f.poster.avif?t=1719456535\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/caaf5bc4188bc6f968096f6cc9c52d0f.webm?t=1719456535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/caaf5bc4188bc6f968096f6cc9c52d0f.mp4?t=1719456535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Red Rock is full of secrets. Break down walls to access unique new areas, each with their own stories hidden amongst the landscape. Venture across the different regions; Kentaro Islands, Celerity Speedway, FMF Outpost and more for you to discover yourself...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/67b7075b9e209df879b6443427c21018.webp?t=1719456535\" width=616 height=44 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/fea0775eb32ae621a4107495cfa155de.poster.avif?t=1719456535\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/fea0775eb32ae621a4107495cfa155de.webm?t=1719456535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/fea0775eb32ae621a4107495cfa155de.mp4?t=1719456535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Survive for as long as possible to achieve the highest score. Compete with friends and see where you stand on the global leaderboards. Only the most skilled pilot can take the top spot!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/2b4e9defae48f04b0c64b914d9bb64cb.webp?t=1719456535\" width=616 height=44 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205520/extras/04729ed5146207c3afbc249818d95c9e.avif?t=1719456535\" width=616 height=290 /></span>",
